text: God Exists, Her Name Is Petrunija () is a 2019 Macedonian Belgian Slovenian Croatian French drama movie directed by Teona Strugar Mitevska and stars Zorica Nusheva, Labina Mitevska, Stefan Vujisic, Suad Begovski. == Other websites == * Category:2019 drama movies Category:Macedonian movies Category:Belgian drama movies Category:Slovenian movies Category:Croatian movies Category:French drama movies
